{"tid":2303522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国2.2億人月收低於500元  已進入「赤貧」狀態","createTime":"2020-11-28T04:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T14:50:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":203,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9dd1975cd4e24986cc8fe65e63e5ceda7b7f38","tid":2303522,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"中國官媒《人民日報》日前發布消息稱，中國832個國家級貧困縣已全部「脫貧摘帽」，全國脫貧攻堅目標任務已經完成，不過多樣數據仍顯示，中國有4.2億人收入低於人民幣800元（約台幣3470元）、2.2億人收入在500元以下（約台幣2168元），546萬人更是沒有任何收入，遠低於世界銀行定義的「貧窮」標準，甚至已進入「赤貧」（極端貧窮）狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/比貧窮更貧窮-中國2-2億人月收低於台幣2000-脫貧摘帽-淪口號-041110898.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%AF%94%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E6%9B%B4%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B2-2%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%88%E6%94%B6%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC%E5%8F%B0%E5%B9%A32000-%E8%84%AB%E8%B2%A7%E6%91%98%E5%B8%BD-%E6%B7%AA%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F-041110898.html&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=d64c5993\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/比貧窮更貧窮-中國2-2億人月收低於台幣2000-脫貧摘帽-淪口號-041110898.html</a>"},{"pid":"b7dc9e00faa2043f037b63bf6312e746bbeaff8e","tid":2303522,"uid":32220,"like":152,"dislike":1,"score":151,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:41:05.000Z","msg":"中國標準10蚊以上就脫貧啦"},{"pid":"333f22d6fb3c4373e75523854c2a6b300336facf","tid":2303522,"uid":121146,"like":112,"dislike":0,"score":112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"貧乜9  佢話富就富啦屌"},{"pid":"9210e115ab4526220149913dfb0108674f6db37a","tid":2303522,"uid":280593,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"奴隸啫,唔計入去㗎"},{"pid":"8e109d8590b9c17e18a1950633ce5470c59151e1","tid":2303522,"uid":346701,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:43:43.000Z","msg":"再嘈月入200就當富人"},{"pid":"50da6a1ff8fa263f368f882842dd65769cab326b","tid":2303522,"uid":28997,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T